These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-1::.
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, orange, broccoli, tomato
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, dancing, reading, hiking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, weightlifting, surfing, tennis
 1. the person who's hobby is reading is in an odd position##4
 2. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person who's sport is surfing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
 4. the person who's sport is handball is not the person eating tomato##6
 5. the person eating broccoli is somewhere to the right of the person eating pomegranate##5
 6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 7. the person who's sport is surfing is not to the left of the person eating orange##8
 8. the person eating orange is not the person who's sport is tennis##6
 9. the person eating pomegranate is not the person who's hobby is hiking##6
10. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
11. the person eating orange is not to the right of the person who's sport is surfing##8
12. the person eating orange is in an even position##4
13. the person eating tomato is not to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##8
14. the person who's hobby is reading is not to the right of the person who's sport is surfing##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Food    | pomegranate         | tomato     | broccoli     | orange         |
| Hobby   | dancing | hiking    | reading     | skydiving |
| Sport   | handball       | weightlifting | tennis | surfing       |

