.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda, lemonade, almond-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, photographer, dressmaker, software-developer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, cycling, rowing, parkour
 1. the dressmaker is not to the right of the software-developer##8
 2. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is the photographer##1
 5. the designer is not the person drinking lemonade##6
 6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the designer##1
 8. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the dressmaker##5
10. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | lemonade          | juice      | almond-milk      | mirinda   |
| Job        | dressmaker     | designer | photographer | software-developer      |
| Sport      | parkour | cycling    | rugby  | rowing |

