.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, magic-tricks, hiking, chess
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, metal, disco, rock
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, train, skateboard, jet-ski
 1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 2. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the person driving the skateboard##5
 3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the fan of rock##1
 4. the fan of metal is somewhere to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##5
 5. the person driving the bus is not the fan of gospel##6
 6. the fan of gospel is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 7. the fan of gospel is not to the right of the fan of rock##8
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the fan of disco##1
 9. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an even position##4
10. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | hiking  | magic-tricks | chess | gardening |
| Music-Genre   | metal  | gospel      | rock | disco        |
| Transport     | bus | skateboard       | jet-ski    | train     |

