.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, drama, time-travel, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, country, indie, hip-hop
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, mexican, egyptian, turkish
 1. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
 2. the mexican is not to the left of the fan of country##8
 3. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere to the right of the person watching superhero movies##5
 4. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching drama movies is not to the right of the mexican##8
 6. the egyptian is not to the right of the person watching western movies##8
 7. the fan of indie is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
 8. the turkish is somewhere to the right of the mexican##5
 9. the indonesian is on the left of the egyptian##1
10. the person watching western movies is the egyptian##1
11. the fan of techno is somewhere to the right of the fan of country##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero   | western | drama    | time-travel |
| Music-Genre   | indie    | country     | techno   | hip-hop     |
| Nationality   | indonesian | egyptian   | mexican | turkish    |

