 1. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
 2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
 5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
 6. the person watching comedy movies is not the person who's hobby is photography##6
 7. the person who's hobby is drawing is not the person who's sport is cricket##6
 8. the person watching animation movies is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 9. the person watching martial-arts movies is not to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##8
10. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's hobby is photography##1
11. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | photography       | drawing | collecting  | sudoku    |
