.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: pear, cherry, spinach, pomegranate
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, fantasy, drama, romance
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, french, indian, egyptian
 1. the person eating spinach is not to the left of the person watching spy movies##8
 2. the person watching romance movies is not the french##6
 3. the indian is somewhere between the person eating cherry and the person watching romance movies##7
 4. the french is not to the left of the person watching fantasy movies##8
 5. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person eating pomegranate##3
 6. the indian is the person watching spy movies##1
 7. the person eating pear is somewhere to the right of the person watching drama movies##5
 8. the egyptian is between the person eating pear and the indian##2
 9. the person watching romance movies is not to the right of the person eating pear##8
10. the person eating spinach is not to the right of the person eating pomegranate##8
11. the nigerian is somewhere to the left of the person watching romance movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Food          | cherry      | spinach      | pomegranate | pear |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | spy    | romance | fantasy     |
| Nationality   | nigerian    | indian | egyptian  | french |

