10. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
11. the person watching epic movies is not to the left of the italian##8
12. the person watching sports movies is not to the left of the person driving the scooter##8
13. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5

