There 4 different types of food: raspberry, watermelon, nectarine, zucchini
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, blues, country, d&b
1. the person eating nectarine is somewhere to the right of the person eating zucchini##5
2. the person eating raspberry is somewhere between the person eating zucchini and the person eating nectarine##7
3. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
4. the fan of country is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
5. the person eating zucchini is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
6. the person eating raspberry is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
7. the person eating zucchini is the fan of blues##1
8. the person eating zucchini is somewhere between the fan of d&b and the person drinking hot-chocolate##7
9. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |     3     |    4     |
