.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, cooking, sudoku, dancing
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, nigerian, chinese, american
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, jet-ski, motorbike, roller
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the right of the person driving the van##8
 2. the american is somewhere between the person driving the roller and the chinese##7
 3. the person who's hobby is cooking is not to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##8
 4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the dutch is not to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
 7. the american is on the left or right of the dutch##3
 8. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5
 9. the person who's hobby is cooking is not to the left of the person driving the van##8
10. the person driving the motorbike is not to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##8
11. the dutch is not to the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##8
12. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
13. the dutch is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
14. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |      3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | filmmaking    | sudoku | dancing | cooking    |
| Nationality   | chinese  | american    | dutch      | nigerian |
| Transport     | jet-ski | van          | roller      | motorbike       |

