 6. the person watching zombie movies is the security-guard##1
 7. the scientist is not to the right of the security-guard##8
 8. the security-guard is not to the left of the person drinking lemonade##8
 9. the security-guard is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5
10. the security-guard is somewhere to the right of the scientist##5
11. the nurse is not the person drinking water##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2   |    3     |      4      |
