 4. the person driving the bus is on the left of the indian##1
 5. the person driving the ship is on the right of the fisherman##1
 6. the designer is on the right of the nurse##1
 7. the pilot is the person driving the ship##1
 8. the person driving the bus is not the fisherman##6
 9. the pilot is not to the left of the british##8
10. the british is not to the right of the fisherman##8
11. the designer is somewhere between the british and the person driving the bus##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |    3     |    4    |
