4. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##5
5. the french is not the person who's sport is snowboarding##6
6. the colombian is between the owner of the hamster and the person who's sport is skiing##2
7. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is climbing##5
8. the french is not to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##8
9. the colombian is on the right of the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | indonesian         | polish       | colombian | french  |
| Pet           | hedgehog        | hamster | snake   | rat   |
| Sport         | sailing | climbing  | snowboarding  | skiing |

