1. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the dutch is not to the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
3. the person who's sport is baseball is between the owner of the goldfish and the owner of the pony##2
4. the german is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
5. the dutch is not the person who's sport is biathlon##6
6. the owner of the pony is on the left of the indian##1
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's sport is water-polo##7
8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
9. the person who's sport is biathlon is the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | dutch | german     | indian  | mexican |
| Pet           | hamster      | pony        | ferret   | goldfish |
| Sport         | water-polo  | biathlon | baseball | parkour       |

 